column8: An uncharted visible wreck was located within the anchorage area to the west of the Keehi Lagoon Barge Channel  the position of the wreck was obtained by several passes with the RESON 8101 multibeam  the hull is visible in the multibeam imagery and a sounding near the bow was designated for positioning.
